Pony Fantasy, an RPG game.

Codename Pancake

Pre-Alpha version
0.0-11r

Uses SFML 2.0-x, not the 2.1 version, it might be updated sometime later.

=======================================

Compiling:

If you wish to compile this, you need to code allowing development from http://www.sfml-dev.org/download/sfml/2.0/
Compile using any compatible C++ compiler, all flags used by SFML are required, 
refer to a tutorial on http://www.sfml-dev.org to figure it out.


Ready-to-run:

An installer will be provided once it's in beta.
